Variables in Stored Procedures
------------------------------

You may declare and use variables within a routine.

* Menu:

* DECLARE Local Variables::     `DECLARE' Local Variables
* SET Statement::               Variable `SET' Statement
* SELECT INTO Statement::       `SELECT ... INTO' Statement


